sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron as cron daemon
    participant Tick as aos tick
    participant FS as runs/ + tick.log
    participant Wrap as wrapper.sh

    Cron->>Tick: invoke at tick_interval
    Tick->>Tick: scan <aos_home>/agents/
    Tick->>FS: LoadRuns(runs/)
    Tick->>Tick: DetectMissed (latest uncovered slot per agent)

    alt new misses found
        Tick->>FS: delete stale miss-*.json for agent
        Tick->>FS: write miss-<agent>-<expectedAt>.json
    else current slot already recorded
        Tick->>Tick: skip (idempotent)
    end

    alt catchup_enabled
        Tick->>Tick: DetectCatchups (latest run == missed?)
        loop per candidate
            Tick->>Wrap: SpawnWrapperDetached (TRIGGER=catch-up)
            Wrap-->>FS: writes <run-id>.json running → success|error
        end
    end

    Tick->>FS: append "[tick] ..." to tick.log
    Tick-->>Cron: exit 0 (stdout: log line or JSON summary)
